#

Butternut Squash and Apple Mash

40 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishHealthyEasy

Description

Creamy, sweet, and savory mash that's perfect as a side dish!

Ingredients

  • butternut squash: 1 medium
  • apple: 1 large
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • cinnamon: 1/4 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: a pinch
